add to a large pot

 - olive oil 
 - 200 g chorizo

cook until starting to crisp
set aside and refrigerate
add to pot

 - 750 g frozen spaghetti vegetable mix 

cook until just starting to brown 
deglaze with

 - 1/4 cup white wine

add

 - 28 oz can drained diced tomatoes 
 - 1 cup chicken stock
 - 1 lbs cubed pork

simmer 3 hours until tender
add

 - 3 19 oz canned drained white beans

add reserved chorizo 
simmer 30 minutes 
serve with
crusty bread 
serves 6-8

#spanish #simple #bulk #slowcooker
